    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>AstraZeneca</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of this study is to evaluate the safety and efficacy of anastrozole 1
      mg given once daily in subjects with McCune-Albright Syndrome.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
