  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>The efficacy of study treatment will be assessed based on the change from baseline measurements relating to vaginal bleeding, bone age, and growth velocity</measure>
    <time_frame>12 months or until the subject demonstrates the lack of efficacy bases upon progression of primary endpoints or experiences serious drug-related toxicity requiring withdrawal</time_frame>
  </primary_outcome>
